Package jwebminer2.gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MetaDataChooserDialog
    A dialog box allowing the user to choose the type of metadata to extract from a file (recording title, artist name, composer name, album title or genre).
    OptionsPanel
    A GUI panel allowing users to choose settings that will govern searches.
    OuterFrame
    The outer component of the jWebMiner GUI that is used to hold tabbed panes and menus.
    ResultsReportPanel
    A JPanel for displaying and saving data.
    SearchWordsPanel
    A GUI panel allowing users to select the search strings to use as a basis for extracting cultural features from the web.
    StringEntryPanel
    A JPanel that stores an editable non-wrapping scrollable JTextArea.
